# isEnabled

**Instance Property**

A Boolean value that indicates whether the track’s container enables it.

## Declaration

```swift
var isEnabled: Bool { get }
```

## Discussion

For file-based media, you can change its [doc://com.apple.avfoundation/documentation/AVFoundation/AVPlayerItemTrack/isEnabled] presentation state using [doc://com.apple.avfoundation/documentation/AVFoundation/AVPlayerItemTrack].
